<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.6.11">
<l>kūntaṉmalar maṅkaikku maṇmaṭan taikkuṅ kulavāyar koḻuntukkuṅ kēḷvaṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>vāynta vaḻuti nāṭaṉ maṉṉu kurukūrc caṭakōpaṉ kuṟṟē valcey</l>
<l>tāynta tamiḻmālai yāyi rattuḷ ḷivaiyu mōrpat tumval lārulaki</l>
<l>lēntu peruñcelvan tārāyt tirumā laṭiyār kaḷaippū cikkanōṟ ṟārkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master all these that are one ten</l>
	<l>among the thousand in a garland of Tamil chosen,</l>
<l>doing menial service, by Caṭakōpaṉ from Kurukūr,</l>
	<l>permanent [in the hand of] the man from the land of excellent Vaḻuti,</l>
<l>on the relative of the flower girl with tresses</l>
	<l>and the earth girl and the tendril of the cowherds in a family,</l>
<l>have practised pūjā for the servants</l>
	<l>of Tirumāl, being a garland of eminent great wealth in the world.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
